Keep the distance maintained between you and the next person but it's okay to be on the same side of the sidewalk as another pedestrian as long as there's space elsewhere on the pavement. Same with getting into queues. You can pass behind people but expect that they are clean but don't high 5 as you pass.

In stores, we have to wait in line and observe the 2-meter-distance sign( If not, just be as close or further away than the person in front of you )

The 4-meter-limit sign just means that a maximum of 4 shoppers are allowed inside the store at once, and by default, please leave 1 meter distance from the person in front.

Restaurants, Casino, Gym, and Sport Centers are open for business, and lastly/the best thing we all have been waiting for, ALL Schools, Universities, KINDERGARTEN, and CRÈCHES are OPEN!!

Shows are back to undergrounds ( Music gets the VIP treatment ).

Bars, restaurants, and pablos are open till 22:00 from Tuesday to Saturday, humid bars are open till 22:00 Monday to Sunday.

Nightclubs, saunas, and similar establishments remain closed.

Ask for the Romer Cup!

Mobile Trade fair is back!
